===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|his||his, its|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{term/t|gem-pro|*hes||of this}}, genitive of {{term/t|gem-pro|*hiz||this, this one}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{term/t|ine-pro|*á¸±e-}}, {{term/t|ine-pro|*á¸±ey-||this}}. Cognate with {{etyl|da|-}}, {{etyl|sv|-}}, {{etyl|no|-}}, {{etyl|is|-}} {{term|hans||his|lang=is}}. More at {{l|en|he}}.

